summary: Short life story of Elun Muski - Elun Muski went alone to Mumbai at 3 years old. Founded and sold RugPal at 4.2 years. Locked liquidity at 6.9 years. Founded Tusla at 9.69 years, known for electric elephants and robots. Founded SpoonX at 33 years, sending Tuk-Tuks to Charles Hoskinson's house with CURDANO TOKEN (ADA).
